{"tid":1660421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嬲同好嬲。","createTime":"2019-10-17T13:20:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T13:35:19.000Z","uid":334979,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d3e05000ab93d92fa46bdf5181ed6211701d5423","tid":1660421,"uid":334979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:20:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/17/210516_92045c7a97952a3013349761d165a0a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F17%2F210516_92045c7a97952a3013349761d165a0a2.jpg&h=7e42fa7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n珍咩惜校園環境下學習？你連自己學生都可以推佢出去死，你仲覺得學生對你哋會有信任？我恨不得炸爛間學院都唔會比死者死得不明不白。<br />\n顛倒事非黑白仲好意思同我講你係教育機構？<br />\n你知唔知咩叫教育？教人冇良知，冇道德，教人冇人性?係唔撚係呀？同我哋講條片冇剪？我剪撚咗你都仲得呀，on系鳩。"},{"pid":"a3ea15145ced88ad4b070069f2b226658fe3fa95","tid":1660421,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:20:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W04Z2Gp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW04Z2Gp.jpg&h=e79a1d2a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4313dc509bbd9c92fcb67589ecaafc7d4067a529","tid":1660421,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:23:34.000Z","msg":"樓主理解力0分"},{"pid":"131b00ff1afdec46d045abbcf40e7bf06f5a17b9","tid":1660421,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:29:57.000Z","msg":"同vtc講教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3fa0593a2d652832732e650ab072d7407e2750b","tid":1660421,"uid":334979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4313dc509bbd9c92fcb67589ecaafc7d4067a529","tid":1660421,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:23:34.000Z","msg":"樓主理解力0分"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:35:19.000Z","msg":"點解咁講，我想聽下"}]}